trans-unit.source: Provides the managed definition of the <see langword="TYMED" /> structure.
trans-unit.target: Fornece a definição gerenciada da estrutura <see langword="TYMED" />.

trans-unit.source: For more information about the `TYMED` structure, see the MSDN Library.
trans-unit.target: Para obter mais informações sobre o `TYMED` estrutura, consulte a biblioteca MSDN.

trans-unit.source: The common language runtime throws an exception when a COM method in native code returns an HRESULT.
trans-unit.target: O common language runtime lança uma exceção quando um método COM em código nativo retorna um HRESULT.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [How to: Map HRESULTs and Exceptions](~/docs/framework/interop/how-to-map-hresults-and-exceptions.md).
trans-unit.target: Para obter mais informações, consulte [como: mapear HRESULTs e exceções](~/docs/framework/interop/how-to-map-hresults-and-exceptions.md).

trans-unit.source: The storage medium is an enhanced metafile.
trans-unit.target: A mídia de armazenamento é um metarquivo avançado.

trans-unit.source: If the <see cref="T:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ComTypes.STGMEDIUM" /><see cref="F:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ComTypes.STGMEDIUM.pUnkForRelease" /> member is <see langword="null" />, the destination process should use <see langword="DeleteEnhMetaFile" /> to delete the bitmap.
trans-unit.target: Se o membro <see cref="T:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ComTypes.STGMEDIUM" /><see cref="F:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ComTypes.STGMEDIUM.pUnkForRelease" /> for <see langword="null" />, o processo de destino deverá usar o <see langword="DeleteEnhMetaFile" /> para excluir o bitmap.

trans-unit.source: The storage medium is a disk file identified by a path.
trans-unit.target: A mídia de armazenamento é um arquivo de disco identificado por um caminho.

trans-unit.source: If the <see langword="STGMEDIUM" /><see cref="F:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ComTypes.STGMEDIUM.pUnkForRelease" /> member is <see langword="null" />, the destination process should use <see langword="OpenFile" /> to delete the file.
trans-unit.target: Se o membro <see langword="STGMEDIUM" /><see cref="F:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ComTypes.STGMEDIUM.pUnkForRelease" /> for <see langword="null" />, o processo de destino deverá usar o <see langword="OpenFile" /> para excluir o arquivo.

trans-unit.source: The storage medium is a Graphics Device Interface (GDI) component (HBITMAP).
trans-unit.target: A mídia de armazenamento é um componente de GDI (Graphics Device Interface) (HBITMAP).

trans-unit.source: If the <see cref="T:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ComTypes.STGMEDIUM" /><see cref="F:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ComTypes.STGMEDIUM.pUnkForRelease" /> member is <see langword="null" />, the destination process should use <see langword="DeleteObject" /> to delete the bitmap.
trans-unit.target: Se o membro <see cref="T:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ComTypes.STGMEDIUM" /><see cref="F:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ComTypes.STGMEDIUM.pUnkForRelease" /> for <see langword="null" />, o processo de destino deverá usar o <see langword="DeleteObject" /> para excluir o bitmap.

trans-unit.source: The storage medium is a global memory handle (HGLOBAL).
trans-unit.target: A mídia de armazenamento é um identificador de memória global (HGLOBAL).

trans-unit.source: Allocate the global handle with the GMEM_SHARE flag.
trans-unit.target: Aloca o identificador global com o sinalizador GMEM_SHARE.

trans-unit.source: If the <see cref="T:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ComTypes.STGMEDIUM" /><see cref="F:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ComTypes.STGMEDIUM.pUnkForRelease" /> member is <see langword="null" />, the destination process should use <see langword="GlobalFree" /> to release the memory.
trans-unit.target: Se o membro <see cref="T:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ComTypes.STGMEDIUM" /><see cref="F:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ComTypes.STGMEDIUM.pUnkForRelease" /> for <see langword="null" />, o processo de destino deverá usar o <see langword="GlobalFree" /> para liberar a memória.

trans-unit.source: The storage medium is a storage component identified by an <see langword="IStorage" /> pointer.
trans-unit.target: A mídia de armazenamento é um componente de armazenamento identificado por um ponteiro <see langword="IStorage" />.

trans-unit.source: The data is in the streams and storages contained by this <see langword="IStorage" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: Os dados estão no fluxos e armazenamentos contidos por essa instância <see langword="IStorage" />.

trans-unit.source: If the <see cref="T:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ComTypes.STGMEDIUM" /><see cref="F:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ComTypes.STGMEDIUM.pUnkForRelease" /> member is not <see langword="null" />, the destination process should use <see langword="IStorage::Release" /> to release the storage component.
trans-unit.target: Se o membro <see cref="T:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ComTypes.STGMEDIUM" /><see cref="F:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ComTypes.STGMEDIUM.pUnkForRelease" /> não for <see langword="null" />, o processo de destino deverá usar o <see langword="IStorage::Release" /> para liberar o componente de memória.

trans-unit.source: The storage medium is a stream object identified by an <see langword="IStream" /> pointer.
trans-unit.target: A mídia de armazenamento é um objeto de fluxo identificado por um ponteiro <see langword="IStream" />.

trans-unit.source: Use <see langword="ISequentialStream::Read" /> to read the data.
trans-unit.target: Usa <see langword="ISequentialStream::Read" /> para ler os dados.

trans-unit.source: If the <see cref="T:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ComTypes.STGMEDIUM" /><see cref="F:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ComTypes.STGMEDIUM.pUnkForRelease" /> member is not <see langword="null" />, the destination process should use <see langword="IStream::Release" /> to release the stream component.
trans-unit.target: Se o membro <see cref="T:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ComTypes.STGMEDIUM" /><see cref="F:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ComTypes.STGMEDIUM.pUnkForRelease" /> não for <see langword="null" />, o processo de destino deverá usar o <see langword="IStream::Release" /> para liberar o componente de fluxo.

trans-unit.source: The storage medium is a metafile (HMETAFILE).
trans-unit.target: A mídia de armazenamento é um metarquivo (HMETAFILE).

trans-unit.source: Use the Windows or WIN32 functions to access the metafile's data.
trans-unit.target: Usa as funções do Windows ou WIN32 para acessar os dados do metarquivo.

trans-unit.source: If the <see cref="T:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ComTypes.STGMEDIUM" /><see cref="F:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ComTypes.STGMEDIUM.pUnkForRelease" /> member is <see langword="null" />, the destination process should use <see langword="DeleteMetaFile" /> to delete the bitmap.
trans-unit.target: Se o membro <see cref="T:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ComTypes.STGMEDIUM" /><see cref="F:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ComTypes.STGMEDIUM.pUnkForRelease" /> for <see langword="null" />, o processo de destino deverá usar o <see langword="DeleteMetaFile" /> para excluir o bitmap.

trans-unit.source: No data is being passed.
trans-unit.target: Nenhum dado está sendo passado.
